# .agents/skillfile — declarative skill list for llm_skills sync
#
# Format: <skill-name>  <git-url-or-rid>  [--project|--global]
# Default target: --project (installs into <project>/.agents/skills/)
#
# Run `scripts/skills-bootstrap.sh` to install/refresh.
#
# The radicle/radboard skills are legacy: this project moved fully to GitHub
# (code + PRs + issues), so they're no longer synced. Their skill directories
# are left in place under .agents/skills/ but are not active.
